com.facebook.buck.rules.modern.builders

Class RemoteExecution

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.modern.builders.RemoteExecution
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IsolatedExecution, Closeable, AutoCloseable

    public final class RemoteExecution
extends Object
implements IsolatedExecution
    An implementation of IsolatedExecution that uses a ContentAddressedStorage and RemoteExecutionService to execute build rules.

    See https://docs.google.com/document/d/1AaGk7fOPByEvpAbqeXIyE8HX_A3_axxNnvroblTZ_6s/preview for a high-level description of the approach to remote execution.
